        "Guest name and credentials",
        "Topic relevance to audience",
        "What makes this conversation unique",
        "Key questions to be explored"
      ],
      "hook": "Why this conversation matters right now"
    },
    {
      "section": "Guest Background & Journey",
      "duration": "2:00-8:00",
      "description": "Explore guest's background and path to expertise",
      "question_categories": [
        "Origin story in their field",
        "Pivotal career moments",
        "Major influences or mentors",
        "Evolution of their thinking"
      ],
      "storytelling": "Create narrative arc from beginnings to current work"
    },
    {
      "section": "Core Topic Deep Dive",
      "duration": "8:00-20:00",
      "description": "Main discussion of the central topic",
      "discussion_techniques": [
        "Start with foundational concepts",
        "Progress to advanced insights",
        "Use examples and case studies",
        "Address common misconceptions"
      ],
      "balance": "Equal speaking time, natural conversation flow"
    },
    {
      "section": "Practical Applications",
      "duration": "20:00-25:00",
