        "Biggest challenges in the field",
        "Unresolved questions",
        "Controversial opinions",
        "Future obstacles"
      ],
      "authenticity": "Don't avoid difficult topics"
    },
    {
      "section": "Future Outlook & Advice",
      "duration": "30:00-35:00",
      "description": "Looking ahead and guidance for viewers",
      "future_topics": [
        "Emerging trends",
        "Technology impacts",
        "Career advice for newcomers",
        "Recommended learning paths"
      ],
      "forward_looking": "Help viewers prepare for what's next"
    },
    {
      "section": "Rapid Fire / Personal Insights",
      "duration": "35:00-38:00",
      "description": "Quick questions for personal insight",
